    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1548180/extras/ee8efb217188accb8cbb701e6e711797.poster.avif?t=1766094280\" width=600 height=536 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1548180/extras/ee8efb217188accb8cbb701e6e711797.webm?t=1766094280\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1548180/extras/ee8efb217188accb8cbb701e6e711797.mp4?t=1766094280\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >披上邪教徒的长袍，拥抱内心的阴暗面，一步一步征服世界。用你的鲜血绘制符文进行血祭，战胜降神道路上遇到的敌人和挑战。遵循你的神的意志，执行恐怖行为，神就会奖励你更强大 的巫术。给无信仰者洗脑，将他们转变成无脑听从你指挥的忠实信徒追随者。他们是没有自我  意志的棋子，愿意为你做任何事。按照神的要求指挥他们行动，甚至祭献他们，以进行更强大  的仪式！<strong>引发世界末日——或者死于尝试的路上</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1548180/extras/eb8648d5c336671a5958dc65ff40d8c4.poster.avif?t=1766094280\" width=600 height=536 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1548180/extras/eb8648d5c336671a5958dc65ff40d8c4.webm?t=1766094280\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1548180/extras/eb8648d5c336671a5958dc65ff40d8c4.mp4?t=1766094280\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Worship》的魅力在于它大胆、亵渎的主题、语气和世界观；在游戏中，你可以找到黑色幽  默的血祭仪式，也能举办奢华的邪恶祭献。《Worship》世界的视觉效果也非常特别，以黑白  墨水素描画风为底，点缀以鲜艳的色彩和手绘动画，搭建起一片诡谲的世界。它的艺术风格既  可爱又独特，遍布游戏的黑暗幽默元素更是使干坏事都变得如此有趣。一个既阴森恐怖又可爱  搞怪的世界正在等待你来探索。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1548180/extras/37e0824f112e5ab9cbc597860ff48b28.poster.avif?t=1766094280\" width=600 height=536 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1548180/extras/37e0824f112e5ab9cbc597860ff48b28.webm?t=1766094280\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1548180/extras/37e0824f112e5ab9cbc597860ff48b28.mp4?t=1766094280\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这款游戏为RPG冒险和roguelike类型带来了全新的（扭曲）解读视角。一个广阔且生动的世  界在游戏里铺开，供你尽情探险。揭露隐藏的秘密，与四大派系互动，培养你的教派：这一切  都是为了让你们对神更加虔诚。当拥有了足够多的信徒、办过足够多的仪式后，你将积攒够力  量，迎接最终考验：召唤邪神降临人间。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>到世界的终末那天，你的虔诚是否足够将邪神请至人间？</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1548180/extras/66d03b5e3059d0c8d447a81698f969b0.avif?t=1766094280\" width=600 height=338 /></span></p>",
